![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/89b6c7c2-6e0d-4561-a62b-7209381d67f7/ep221.jpg)

EAT PEACE MOTHERFU\*#ER! That's usually the last thing someone hears before being taken out by Christopher Smith, The Peacemaker. In this episode, we discuss the first season of Peacemaker, debate John Cena's acting skills and Vigilante quotes, and get into the mess that is the current DCEU. We talk that opener, those butterflies, and what is the appropriate time to rock! Do you really wanna taste it? I don't know but you DO wanna HEAR IT, so check out the latest episode of the Major Issues Podcast talking all things Peacemaker!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
